{"tid":697231,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想養竉物 求意見","createTime":"2018-06-10T21:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T09:06:15.000Z","uid":14817,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7fbb68066ade5c7a6a3b4b37199ddde8db864b56","tid":697231,"uid":14817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T21:14:34.000Z","msg":"之前住香港果陣有養過倉鼠<br />\n後黎老死就冇養了<br />\n<br />\n依家住澳洲有花園仔<br />\n想養返隻互動性高既竉物<br />\n短時間唔會返香港<br />\n想養壽命5年以下既竉物<br />\n<br />\n最好係可以訓練既品種<br />\n有見過鄰居養松鼠<br />\n我暫時唔想養貓狗鼠<br />\n每月會留約3500左右比佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不接受人類"},{"pid":"a9e5e38f50e754b6c34c79ac76f6fc55e9d9050b","tid":697231,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T23:18:14.000Z","msg":"壽命五年下 不如你講下有咩動物"},{"pid":"434616c4f1cf20a2a32b057c4de34bd9913ba6df","tid":697231,"uid":78971,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔係因為想養咩而決定養<br />\n而係想養先諗養咩"},{"pid":"8051e0beb6f9b554d040f172cd20f7a144786dd7","tid":697231,"uid":78971,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:13:07.000Z","msg":"拍下散拖算啦<br />\n5年內分手<br />\n每月預$3500喺佢身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無謂害咗隻動物呀"},{"pid":"8d6125db94dea12288f935871f17d8a84c3661d3","tid":697231,"uid":150595,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:16:30.000Z","msg":"五年你想訓練啲乜出來？<br />\n試下<br />\nPokemon?"},{"pid":"0203dd3e8a078d2b203334eb09a40c77de200129","tid":697231,"uid":90820,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:15:44.000Z","msg":"萬一佢好命<br />\n唔止5年命嘅話<br />\n樓主離開澳洲嗰時<br />\n諗住棄養定殺咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7feeecb2f8285e18583af061e9088ebc9a403e8","tid":697231,"uid":3167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:21